This is a BepInEx (>647) mod to increase monster item drop rates.

Rate multiplier from 1-1000. Lowest drop rate of items is 0.1% so 1000 guarantees all monster drops.

[b]Install[/b]
[list]
[*]Install [url=https://builds.bepinex.dev/projects/bepinex_be]BepInEx BE[/url] version 647 or later (IL2CPP_x64) or install other base mod BepInEx already included (like [url=https://github.com/Lyall/RF5Fix]original RF5Fix v0.1.5 mod[/url] or my [url=https://github.com/davidthemaster30/RF5Fix]updated RF5Fix mod[/url])[/*]
[*]Extract the contents of downloaded zip:
[list]
[*] put .dll into [b]<GameDirectory>\BepInEx\plugins[/b][/*]
[*](Optional, if not copied, will be generated after first launch) put .cfg into [b]<GameDirectory>\BepInEx\config[/b][/*]
[/list]
[/*]
[*](Optional) Install [url=https://github.com/BepInEx/BepInEx.ConfigurationManager]BepInEx Configuration Manager v18.3[/url], there is a bug with the current version of the mod that requires this mod[/*]
[*](Optional) Install [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/runefactory5/mods/95]Autopickup changed to pickup branches and rocks dropped by monsters[/url][/*]
[/list]


[b]Uninstall[/b]
Remove the dll and the cfg files. The mod does not change any file.

Code available here:
[url=https://github.com/davidthemaster30/RF5-AutoPickup]https://github.com/davidthemaster30/RF5-AutoPickup[/url]